Media
Manga
Kings of My Love ran in the manga magazine Ciao since October 1, 2009 and ended on June 3, 2014. There are twelve bound volumes in total. A sequel Ore-sama Kingdom DX started in Ciao DX on March 19, 2020. One volume was published in March 2021.
